query:
INSERT INTO computations (
                tenant_id,
                output_handle,
                dependencies,
                fhe_operation,
                is_scalar,
                dependence_chain_id,
                transaction_id,
                is_allowed,
                created_at,
                schedule_order,
                is_completed
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9::timestamp, $9::timestamp, $10)
            ON CONFLICT (tenant_id, output_handle, transaction_id) DO NOTHING
